The Postmaster of Mafdet has received a route commission for a complete survey of the Great Oasis. Caravans operating between Mafdet and the interior oases depend on current navigation data, and the Great Oasis has no recent comprehensive record in the harbor authority's reference files. Map every accessible section of the oasis and return with a complete route record.
Your Great Oasis survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority. The postmaster has forwarded the route documentation to caravan operators registered for interior oasis routes, and dispatch scheduling has already been updated to reflect the new survey data.

